{"type":null,"faqId":10159,"title":"G6-U00省电小窍门","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（1）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">不使用手机时，按电源键关闭屏幕。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（2）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">缩短屏幕休眠时间：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>显示</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>休眠</b>，设置屏幕休眠时间。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（3）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">降低屏幕亮度：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>显示</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>亮度</b>，设置屏幕亮度。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（4）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭蓝牙和<span>WLAN</span>：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b>，在<b>无线和网络</b>区域关闭蓝牙和<span>WLAN</span>。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（5）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭后台数据同步：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>帐户</b>，关闭帐户与同步。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（6）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭数据业务：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>移动网络</b>，关闭<b>始终连接数据业务</b>开关。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（7）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭<span>GPS</span>：在主屏幕，点击</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';font-size:12pt;\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">-&gt;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">全部</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">-&gt;</span><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">位置信息访问权限</span></b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，关闭<b>访问我的位置信息</b>开关。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（8）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">手机休眠关闭应用：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:10pt;\">在主屏幕，最左边一页，点击<b>“手机管理”文件夹<span>-&gt;</span>手机管家<span>-&gt;</span>省电管理<span>-&gt;</span>受保护的后台应用</b>：列表中的应用（点击“手动添加”可以添加应用）表示休眠时不会被清理，点击“禁止”应用程序会从列表中删除。</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"696","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396603796000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":15,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"省电小窍门","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}